## Restrictions on solver dependencies (PRD §6.3 algorithm license whitelist)

- **EPL-2.0** (IPOPT / Bonmin / Couenne): called as library only; NO modification or fork.
- **GPL-3.0** (ECOS): **NOT enabled until M0 wk2 legal sign-off**. SCS (MIT) is preferred fallback.
- **Commercial** (Gurobi / SCIP): NOT used in this project.

See `license-allowed.txt` and `scripts/check_licenses.sh` for CI enforcement.
